<template>
  <form>
    <label></label>
    <input
      type="text"
      :name="formData.queryField.name"
      :id="formData.queryField.id"
      v-model="formData.queryField.value"
    />
  </form>
</template>
<script setup>
import { reactive } from "vue";

const formData = reactive({
  queryField: {
    label: "Query",
    name: "query",
    id: "query",
    validations: [{ required: true, message: "Query is Required" }],
    value: "",
  },
});
</script>
